    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly,</>I assume everyone knows this because I usually figure things out later than other foodies, but did you know if you want your avocado to ripen on command, you leave it near bananas?</>They put out some kind of pheromone that causes avocadoes to ripen!!</>I leave my avos in the fridge until the morning of the day I want to eat them, then take them out and leave them near a bunch of ripening bananas on the counter &#8211; by that evening or the next morning (depending on how soft you want them) they are ready!!</p>
    </div>

